videos.headline: Asberry's over-the-shoulder catch extends Army's lead
videos.description: Army QB Chris Carter throws a 59-yard pass to RB Jordan Asberry, who tracks the ball, catches it over his shoulder, and runs into the end zone to increase their lead to 35-0 over Lafayette.
